<br>
&lt;b&gt;Lightning Call&lt;/b&gt;  <br>
(Level 19)<br>
<br>
122 DD, with Knockback/Stun<br>
Indoors and Outdoors<br>
<br>
This is a second indoor-usable stun for druids, a lower level version of Fury of Air.  It saves at MR + 25, so it's as resisty as Breath of Ro (Fury saves at MR + 15, which is slightly harder to resist), but will come in useful when you are faced with a known gater or CHer.<br>
